There are several ways in which tourism affects our area. The main, and most obvious is the landscape itself but there are however other attractions in the area.
Number 1:-{New Forest Butterfly Farm.
This is not an ordinary farm. This farm produces and looks after many beautiful and varied butterfies. Some of these are endangered spieces. {(Section 8)}
Number 2:-{Ashurst camp site.}
This is only really a caravan site for the use of people on holiday in the area. The campsite holds about 2000 caravans {(Sections 5)}
